item.title: [+864] Christian researcher: Jesus did not die on a cross
item.description: The crucifixion is apparently under review. In his doctoral thesis, newly graduated Swedish theologian Gunnar Samuelsson argues that there is absolutely no historical evidence that crucifixion was used for executions at the time of Jesus Christ's death. In original Greek version of the Bible, there isn't even a mention of a cross.
